To keep the wolf from the door
run out of money: hết tiền
authentic real English: tiếng anh đích thực
miserable: khổ sở
plumber: thợ sửa ống nước
When people say they're trying to keep the wolf from the door they mean they've only just got enough money to survive.
struggle: đấu tranh
spare: dự phòng

Give me credit
impressive: ấn tượng
To give me credit means give me praise or appreciation for something I've done
praise: khen
appreciation: đánh giá cao
deserve: xứng đáng
